Shadownav

What the project is for
	Bootstrap navbar and dropdown shadow effects plugin
		-Works with default, static top and fixed navbars ( See https://getbootstrap.com/docs/3.4/getting-started/#examples-navbars )

How to configure and install it
	Markup
		1. Wrap nav with Shadownav wrapper
			-.sn-default for (default) navbar
			-.sn-static for static top navbar
			-.sn-fixed for fixed navbar
		2. Wrap .dropdown-menu element with a div
		3. Wrap .dropdown-menu a elements text contents with divs

An example of how to use it or get it running
	https://tightcode.github.io/shadownav

